---

## 📖 Overview

This repository contains my Lab 06 project focused on **Authentication Attacks**. The objective of this lab was to understand how attackers obtain credentials, recover passwords, dump authentication secrets, and perform both offline and online password attacks in a controlled penetration testing environment.

All activities were conducted in an isolated lab environment for educational purposes only.

---

## 🎯 Learning Objectives

- Understand Windows authentication mechanisms
- Extract credentials from system memory
- Recover and crack password hashes
- Perform offline password cracking
- Demonstrate online password attacks
- Evaluate authentication weaknesses
- Recommend defensive security controls

